# Core Package Import Rules

When importing React components from the `@bracketbear/core` package, always import from the `/react` subpath:

```typescript
// ✅ Correct - import from /react subpath
import { Ticker, BracketBearLogo } from '@bracketbear/core/react';

// ❌ Incorrect - import from root
import { Ticker, BracketBearLogo } from '@bracketbear/core';
```

This ensures proper tree-shaking and avoids importing unnecessary Astro-specific components when working with React components.

## Examples of React components that should use /react path:
- Ticker
- BracketBearLogo  
- Button
- ValidatedForm
- TextInput
- TextareaInput
- CheckboxInput
- CheckboxField
- Field
- PointerFX
- SkillPill

## Astro components should use root import:
- Layout
- ContentLayout
- NavBar
- Footer
- DetailBlock
- SummaryBlock
